  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"zSiRaB-B\">我会先变成女的，</p><p data-pid=\"GHswYeNc\">毕竟我很期待我的女性角色是什么样的。</p><p data-pid=\"7gBQ4chM\">她大概温文尔雅吧，毕竟我是个风雅的人。</p><p data-pid=\"v0owDZBf\">然后我会远离人群，</p><p data-pid=\"LskYcsTV\">不时以另外一种身份出现。</p><p data-pid=\"B564eGhL\">以女性角色来等作恶者自己上门</p><p data-pid=\"9VY3UpWn\">再用男性角色施以重拳</p><p data-pid=\"JGybjA2o\">法律太迟，不如我来。</p><p data-pid=\"F3yCCBHi\">毕竟天天健身，总得为社会做点事。</p><p data-pid=\"M3_OAKWF\">如果能自由切换就太好了，我就可以明白女性到底是怎么思考的，身体结构是什么样的</p><p data-pid=\"gsicBHSk\"><b><i>对了，人妖算性别吗？</i></b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2048\" data-rawheight=\"1085\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a20644e1bf9e810a472f4b279835d48_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2048\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2048\" data-rawheight=\"1085\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a20644e1bf9e810a472f4b279835d48_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2048\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1ac1f8dcc573d05254e2208344061cd0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"1085\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"mTfTuY4h\"><b><i>当然不会出现让兄弟们爽爽这种事...</i></b></p><p></p></span><spa